author: Y Combinator
description:
The U.S. government spends $100B+ a year on consulting—most of it inefficient. With LLMs and political pressure to cut waste, there’s a huge opportunity to replace legacy consulting with AI-powered software. We’re looking to fund startups taking on this space.

Apply to YC Fall 2025 at ycombinator.com/apply.
title: Using LLMs Instead of Government Consulting
